                    </div>
                    <span>Do yourself a favor and don't waste your money on this thing like I did. It's not worth reading. The coverage of the API is incomplete, to put it nicely, and the explanations are convoluted and confusing. Not worth the money at all.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A pathetic excuse for a book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
